  • Classes in org.vngx.jsch used by org.vngx.jsch 
    Class and Description
    Buffer
    A simple byte Buffer implementation which wraps a byte array and provides commonly used functionality for accessing and setting values according to the SSH spec for packets.
    Channel
    Default base implementation of a SSH channel and provides a centralized pool for tracking all channel instances.
    ChannelForwardedTCPIP
    Implementation of Channel for server-to-client forwarded connections over TCP/IP.
    ChannelSftp.LsEntry
    Represents an entry returned by the 'ls' SFTP command containing information about a file or folder on the remote system.
    ChannelType
    Enum constants to represent the available Channel types.
    JSch
    Factory for creating instances of Session and provides some general static methods for working with the vngx-jsch library.
    Packet
    Implementation of an SSH2 binary data packet.
    Session
    TODO Add support for setting a ThreadFactory instance for creating all sub threads in session and its channels TODO Add a reset method which resets all the state variables after disconnecting from the SSH server or when the connect method runs
    SftpATTRS
    Attribute information for a path as retrieved from the sftp session.
    SftpProgressMonitor
    Interface for displaying the progress of an SFTP operation.
    UserInfo
    An interface defining an API for a user interface to retrieve user input and display messages.
